  • Enclosing class:
    InputLayout

    public static class InputLayout.LayoutParams
extends FrameLayout.LayoutParams
    Per-child layout information for child views of InputLayout.

    See Layout Attributes for a list of all child view attributes that this class supports.

    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
